# ============================================================
# St Kevin's Hampton Park — Admin IP Whitelist
# ============================================================
# STATUS: DISABLED
# The whitelist block below is commented out.
# Activate it once you have the school's static IP address.
#
# HOW TO ACTIVATE:
#   1. Replace SCHOOL_IP_HERE with the school's static IP
#      (e.g.  Require ip 203.0.113.45)
#   2. Add any additional IPs (developer, principal's home, etc.)
#   3. Uncomment the <RequireAny> block
#   4. Re-upload this file to the server via cPanel File Manager
#
# FINDING SCHOOL IP: Ask your ISP or visit whatismyip.com
# from a computer on the school's network.
# ============================================================

# Prevent directory listing
Options -Indexes

# Custom error page for blocked IPs (file lives outside /admin/)
ErrorDocument 403 /admin-blocked.html

# ── Uncomment the block below to activate IP whitelisting ──
#
# <RequireAny>
#   Require ip SCHOOL_IP_HERE
#   Require ip DEV_IP_HERE
# </RequireAny>
